; Coverage test for xact.cc line 1117-1118
; Tests auto-xact where the auto posting itself has an explicit cost.
; When post->cost is set, it is copied directly to new_post->cost
; without deriving from annotations.

= Expenses:Food
    Liabilities:Tax  $5.00 @ 1 EUR
    Assets:Tax       -5 EUR

2024/03/01 Test
    Expenses:Food     $100.00
    Assets:Checking

test reg --generated
24-Mar-01 Test                  Expenses:Food               $100.00      $100.00
                                Assets:Checking            $-100.00            0
                                Liabilities:Tax               $5.00        $5.00
                                Assets:Tax                   -5 EUR        $5.00
                                                                          -5 EUR
end test
